song_lyrics: Man Mohan ke lāl adharko, pūran te ras pīno... 1
Shyām sundar toy pal nahī chhorat, rasik chhel ranga bhīno... 2
Tose khelat Shyām chatur var, dhan dhan kahe lok tīno... 3
Brahmānand kahe Hari toku, nij mukh āsan dīno... 4
title: Kaun mahā tap kīno moraliyā
